Class Event

java.lang.Object
Event
All Implemented Interfaces:
Comparable<Event>
Direct Known Subclasses:
Social, Talk
public class Event extends Object implements Comparable<Event>
This class blueprints what a generic event would look like. It implements the comparable interface so that events can be compared to one another for sorting

1 30/03/2022
